2008-01-29 Version v0.2:
	- Comments for event->command mapping
	- 'Sticky' profile
	- Macros support
	- Print joystick mode (-e argument)
	- Execute command mode (-x argument)
	- Better usage text
	- ${profile} variable

2008-10-11 Version v0.1:
	- Do not require Linux::Joystick module
	- Fixed memory leak caused by Linux::Joystick
	- Added some stuff to make intergration with gleanstick possible
	- Added the stick move events
	- Keep track of active profile in /tmp/leanstick.active

2008-01-26 Version v0.01:
	- Initial release
